<h2>Canada Olympic Park is looking for VOLUNTEERS</h2>
<p><font size="2">Summer Volunteer Opportunities for students 13 yrs. and older will include:
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hosts in the Olympic Hall of Fame and Museum</p>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Counsellors in Training – Summer Adventure Camp</p>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Assistant Pros – Mountain Bike Camps</p>
<p>Once a volunteer completes a min. of 60 volunteer hours within the fiscal year (April 1 – March 31), they are eligible for a season’s pass and site discounts provided they remain active as a volunteer.</p>
<p><strong><em>See Mrs. Allen for more Information</em></strong></p>
</font></p>
